============================================================
Third-party protocol references
============================================================

Some vendor drivers in solar_monitor/vendors/ document register
maps and protocol details cross-referenced against the following
open-source projects and public protocol documents. Register
definitions are facts, not creative expression; field names and
structure are paraphrased to canonical WattPost metrics.

  EG4 / Luxpower inverter driver (vendors/eg4)
    - joyfulhouse/eg4_web_monitor              (MIT)
    - celsworth/lxp-bridge                     (MIT)
    - EG4 18kPV-12LV Modbus Protocol PDF       (publicly mirrored)

  Deye / Sunsynk / Sol-Ark driver pair (vendors/deye)
    - kellerza/sunsynk                         (Apache-2.0)
    - StephanJoubert/home_assistant_solarman   (Apache-2.0)
    - Deye Modbus PDF (mirrored at domotica.solar)

  Voltronic / Axpert / MPP Solar / EG4 6500EX (vendors/voltronic)
    - Voltronic Inverter Communication Protocol v3.6 (vendor doc)
    - Community rebadge reports (Axpert, MPP Solar PIP/LV-MK,
      EG4 6000XP/6500EX, Mecer, RCT, Infinisolar, etc.)

  JK BMS driver (vendors/jkbms)
    - syssi/esphome-jk-bms                     (MIT)

  JBD / Overkill Solar BMS driver (vendors/jbd)
    - Overkill Solar published protocol docs
    - syssi/esphome-jbd-bms                    (MIT)

  Daly BMS driver (vendors/daly)
    - dalybms.com published protocol docs
    - bigmonkeyboy/daly-bms-uart               (community)

  AiLi smart shunt driver (vendors/aili)
    - ChrisAndrews-Photos/aili-shunt           (community)
    - somewattsolar/aili-shunt-mqtt            (community)

  Junctek smart shunt driver (vendors/junctek)
    - Community ASCII-protocol reverse engineering

  EPEVER / EPSolar Tracer MPPT driver (vendors/epever)
    - EPEVER Modbus protocol PDF               (vendor doc)

  Renogy driver families (vendors/renogy)
    - cyrils/renogy-bt protocol reverse engineering
      (parsers ported in; no runtime dependency)

  Victron VE.Direct + Instant Readout drivers (vendors/victron)
    - Victron VE.Direct Protocol PDF           (vendor doc)
    - victron-ble Python reference             (encryption format)

  Mopeka tank-level driver (vendors/mopeka)
    - Mopeka BLE advertisement format          (public)

  Govee + Ruuvi ambient sensor drivers (transport/ble_*)
    - Community advertisement-format documentation

